Title: An Act Changing the Name of the San Mateo Elementary School in the Municipality of Aleosan, Province of North Cotabato, to Aleosan Central Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 773
An Act Changing the Name of the San Mateo Elementary School in the Municipality of Aleosan, Province of North Cotabato, to Aleosan Central Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the San Mateo Elementary School in the Municipality of Aleosan, Province of North Cotabato, is changed to Aleosan Central Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
